    "Name": "Kuma",
    "Details": "A slightly less mobile but more heavily armed variant, the Kuma 2 replaced the heavier Improved Jump Jets with standard versions which reduced its jump distance to 180 meters. The weight saved allowed the replacement of the Heavy Large Laser with a Plasma Cannon with two tons of ammunition, and a 9-Tubed Advanced Tactical Missile Launcher with four tons of ammunition.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Laser</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
